# Story 2.5: Enable Drill-Down Navigation

## Story Metadata
- **Epic:** 2 - Dashboard & KPIs
- **Status:** done
- **Implemented:** 2025-12-28
- **Session:** SESSION-004

## User Story
As **Gabriel (Fleet Manager)**,
I want **to drill down from dashboard to detailed views**,
So that **I can investigate specific areas of concern**.

## Acceptance Criteria

| AC | Criteria | Status |
|----|----------|--------|
| AC1 | Click variance KPI -> Balancing page | PASS |
| AC2 | Click depot card -> Map filtered to depot | PASS |
| AC3 | Click maintenance alert -> Gantt filtered | PASS |
| AC4 | Navigation preserves context | PASS |

## Implementation Details

### Files Modified
- `apps/web/src/components/dashboard/DashboardKPIs.tsx` - Added navigation
- `apps/web/src/components/dashboard/DepotCapacityCards.tsx` - Added navigation
- `apps/web/src/components/dashboard/MaintenanceAlerts.tsx` - Added navigation

### Navigation Patterns
```typescript
// Variance KPI click
router.push('/balancing');

// Depot card click
router.push(`/map?depot=${depot.id}`);

// Maintenance alert click
router.push(`/maintenance?train=${train.id}`);
```

### Context Preservation
- URL query parameters for filters
- Next.js shallow routing for performance

## Dev Notes
Drill-down creates natural flow from overview to detail.
